  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (08a629a 2023-06-03T00:14:26.563741000Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nanvil  --base-fee 0\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nAnvil rejects transactions priced at `0 gwei` when `--base-fee 0`. It fails with\r\n> Error: processing response error (body=\"{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"id\\\":72,\\\"error\\\":{\\\"code\\\":-32003,\\\"message\\\":\\\"max fee per gas less than block base fee\\\"}}\", error={\"code\":-32003}, requestBody=\"{\\\"method\\\":\\\"eth_sendRawTransaction\\\"\r\n\r\n\r\nFirst noticed this with forge 0.2.0 (cc5637a 2023-06-02T00:22:41.615504000Z)",
